{"tid":757974,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"自爆作嘔 又叫囡囡學做姐姐！吳若希 暗示又有咗？","createTime":"2018-07-27T09:33:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T04:52:42.000Z","uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"89f4fc00983817aefadaed7ed625dd9453aeb59e","tid":757974,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T09:33:03.000Z","msg":"歌手吳若希(Jinny)上年同老公何兆鴻(Alex) 奉女成婚，不過已為人母嘅Jinny講過老公一直未有求婚，日前Alex話老公忽然補番求婚儀式，仲無限放閃話「希望能拿餘生報答你的愛」。驚喜嘅事何止咁少，早幾日，Jinny仲喺IG自爆作嘔，又晒淼淼新相仲叮囑佢快啲學做好姐姐，唔通放風暗示有咗？！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吳若希自從有咗BB後搬咗去澳門同Alex一齊住，即使陀住BB到之後生完復工，都係經常港澳兩邊走，搭船過大海當食生菜，不過日前佢自爆搭船暈船浪作嘔，當時已有網友問佢係咪有咗⋯<br />\n<br />\n之後Jinny喺IG上載張淼淼同另一位小朋友同狗仔玩嘅相，留言話：「看到小可愛們的互動，都可以感受到滿滿的愛！喬喬一定會是一個很好的姐姐！淼淼也要快點努力學當一個好姐姐」唔止作嘔，又叫囡囡學做好姐姐？唔少網友見到Jinny咁講，估佢係咪有第二胎，紛紛向佢送上恭喜同祝福！"},{"pid":"c24238331778ac2934f71cfd8e04ef64a8f8d957","tid":757974,"uid":195009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T09:37:01.000Z","msg":"幫人養2個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7241d19a9bcd9a1063c042a91cdee056945c08ce","tid":757974,"uid":82917,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T09:40:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/174035_c99cc1a28387d6403648c930dc51a151.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F174035_c99cc1a28387d6403648c930dc51a151.png&h=a90907da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95f49b686ad851386be8695dbc1101ec1999d706","tid":757974,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7241d19a9bcd9a1063c042a91cdee056945c08ce","tid":757974,"uid":82917,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T09:40:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/174035_c99cc1a28387d6403648c930dc51a151.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F174035_c99cc1a28387d6403648c930dc51a151.png&h=a90907da&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T09:42:56.000Z","msg":"何生對何太真係好"},{"pid":"7ca89036fbc485c2458840324a81aca62017c7db","tid":757974,"uid":138649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T12:05:17.000Z","msg":"囡似爸爸 一家人真幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2216db9ad918b020e38a7712aee9c9ca6b8e3f55","tid":757974,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T04:52:42.000Z","msg":"有能力生多幾日. 都係好事. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}